Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:53.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5\bord0.1\fn0TOMQ3NR\fs70\c&HF9F8F2&\3c&H000000&\pos(965,990)}龙宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.59,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fnSE1I3K0X\frz347.4\fax0.25\c&H847F82&\pos(405,1020)}禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:45.89,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur0.5\fnSE1I3K0X\fs75\c&H1BB0FC&}嘿咻 嘿咻
